body:
Adds a couple of new versions to the py-aiohttp package, with the corresponding dependencies.

(@adamjstewart the dependencies should be correct this time, but I didn't add intermediate versions between 3.6.2 and 3.7.4, contrary to the previous PR).

EDIT: actually the following PR needs to be merged first: https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/28194
title: [py-aiohttp] added new version
